This is my first time buying textured vinyl, I was worried about the texture and quality but I'm glad to see that the quality is really good. The sheet has a real wood like texture with grooves and cuts, the color is very nice. The back side of the sheet has a scale pattern for measurement. Using them was a very fun experiment for me.
Overall its a great product i used this sticker sheet to renovate one of very old table top and it really worked for me..... So i recommend it.
